<div class="sections">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="information left">
        <h3>Start making money again!</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Install in seconds. Copy and paste!</strong>
            <div>
              No need to rewrite your advertising code base. Just
              paste in our script before any other ad code and 
              we will take care of the rest. 
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Retain non-paying users.</strong>
            <div>
              Asking users to disable Ad Blockers only
