              your non-paying users. Use them as an engine for word of mouth 
              growth while still keeping the lights on.
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Let us fight the good fight for you.</strong>
            <div>
              Ensuring your ads are delivered is a tick tac toe game
              with Ad Blockers. They are constantly improving their
              blocking engine, doing everything in their power to
              cut off a source of revenue. You need a team that will be 
              there to out think their moves. We are here to fight those 
              battles so you can focus on what matters most. 
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="code right">
        <div class="sample">
          <pre><code><%= include("../samples/html") %></code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
